'''塞維爾縣'''（{{lang en|'''Sevier County'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]西南部的一個縣，该县西鄰[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]，面積1,506平方公里。根据[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，该縣共有人口17,058人。<ref>[http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ 2010 census data] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706203009/http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ |date=2011-07-06 }}</ref>该縣縣治為[[德昆|德昆]]（{{lang|en|De Queen}}）。{{GR|6}}该縣亦是一個[[禁酒|禁酒]]的縣。<ref>Winn, Russell and Giacopassi, David. Effects of county-level alcohol prohibition on motor vehicle accidents. ''Social Science Quarterly'', 1993, ''74'', 783–792.</ref>

==歷史==
[[File:ChrisLitherlandDeQueen.jpg|thumb]]
塞維爾縣於1828年10月17日根據立法授權成立，是自[[亨普斯特德縣|亨普斯特德縣]]和[[米勒縣_(阿肯色州)|米勒縣]]成立的，亦是阿肯色州第16個成立的縣。<ref>{{cite journal|last1= Strickland|first1= Rex W.|title= Miller County, Arkansas Territory: The Frontier That Men Forgot|journal= Chronicles of Oklahoma|volume= 19|issue= 1|page= 43|publisher= Oklahoma Historical Society|url= http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Chronicles/v019/v019p037.html|accessdate= 2012-05-13|date= March 1941|author= |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120728082850/http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Chronicles/v019/v019p037.html|archive-date= 2012-07-28|dead-url= yes}} (footnote 17)</ref>5天後，立法機關擴大了本縣的版圖，將[[红河_(密西西比河)|红河]]以南的土地納入本縣內。<ref>{{cite journal|last1= Strickland|first1= Rex W.|title= Miller County, Arkansas Territory: The Frontier That Men Forgot|journal= Chronicles of Oklahoma|volume= 19|issue= 1|page= 43|publisher= Oklahoma Historical Society|url= http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Chronicles/v019/v019p037.html|accessdate= 2012-05-13|date= March 1941|author= |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120728082850/http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Chronicles/v019/v019p037.html|archive-date= 2012-07-28|dead-url= yes}}</ref>本縣的政府於11月1日正式生效。<ref>{{cite book |title= The American Counties: Origins of County Names, Dates of Creation, and Population Data, 1950-2000 |url= https://archive.org/details/americancounties0000kane |edition= 5th|last= Kane|first= Joseph Nathan|last2= Aiken|first2= Charles Curry |year= 2005|publisher= [[Rowman_&_Littlefield|Scarecrow Press]]|location= [[Oxford|Oxford, England]]|isbn= 0810850362|page= [https://archive.org/details/americancounties0000kane/page/274 274]}}</ref>縣名紀念[[美國參議院|聯邦參議員]]、駐[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]大使[[安布羅西·H·塞維爾|安布羅西·H·塞維爾]] （{{lang|en|Ambrose Hundley Sevier}}）。<ref>Kane, J. N. and C. C. Aiken. The American Counties: Origins of County Names Dates of Creation and Population Data 1950-2000. Lanham, MD.: Scarecrow Press, 2005.</ref>

自本縣成立以來，縣治已經更換了好幾次。本縣的第一個縣治為帕拉克利夫特（{{lang|en|Paraclifta}}）。於1871年，洛克家族（{{lang|en|Lockes}}）捐出了{{convert|120|acre|km2}}土地予塞維爾縣政府。作為報答，縣政府將縣治遷往洛克堡（{{lang|en|Lockesburg}}）。於1905年，縣政府將縣治遷往德昆。

