  |url=http://www.census.gov/tiger/tms/gazetteer/county2k.txt
  |title=Census 2000 U.S. Gazetteer Files: Counties
  |publisher=United States Census
  |accessdate=2011-02-13
  |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68EB8WXmf?url=http://www.census.gov/tiger/tms/gazetteer/county2k.txt
  |archive-date=2012-06-06
  |dead-url=yes
  }}</ref>塞維爾縣有著「湖泊之地」（{{lang|en|The Land of Lakes}}）、「水果鮮花之地」（{{lang|en|The Land of Fruits and Flowers}}）和「友好人們的家」（{{lang|en|The Home of Friendly People}}）的綽號。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.maplandia.com/united-states/arkansas/sevier-county/de-queen/register/ |title=Register at De Queen, Sevier County, Arkansas, United States |access-date=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013039/http://www.maplandia.com/united-states/arkansas/sevier-county/de-queen/register/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>本縣有「湖泊之地」的綽號是因為本縣擁有五個半徑約為{{convert|35|mi|km|adj=on}}的湖泊。此外，本縣亦擁有五條河流和很多山區溪流和森林。<ref>[http://soildatamart.nrcs.usda.gov/manuscripts/AR133/0/SEVIER.pdf Soil Survey of Sevier County, Arkansas] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130216200324/http://soildatamart.nrcs.usda.gov/manuscripts/AR133/0/SEVIER.pdf |date=2013-02-16 }}</ref>

